name: VLC Cornet Fried Cone
description: Real ephemeral street art sticker on a wall in the city of Paris. The cone obsession collection is an official production of NFT streetart by the non-profit association VLC (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VideoLAN) 3 billion people have already seen our traffic logo Cone, share our cone addiction by collecting our unique works, real ephemeral stickers in the streets of the city of Paris. The money collected will be used to add new features to our open source software!
